      <p id="Par56">J-SPACE reconstructs the phylogenetic tree of the sampled cells by computing their <italic>genealogy tree</italic>, i.e., a graph <inline-formula id="IEq15"><alternatives><tex-math id="M29">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
