				\begin{document}$${{\mathcal {D}}}{{\mathcal {A}}}_m$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M42"><mml:mrow><mml:mi mathvariant="script">D</mml:mi><mml:msub><mml:mi mathvariant="script">A</mml:mi><mml:mi>m</mml:mi></mml:msub></mml:mrow></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="12859_2022_4779_Article_IEq21.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> the list of the labels of the two nodes occupied in the <inline-formula id="IEq22"><alternatives><tex-math id="M43">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
