				\begin{document}$${\mathcal {T}}_m$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M46"><mml:msub><mml:mi mathvariant="script">T</mml:mi><mml:mi>m</mml:mi></mml:msub></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="12859_2022_4779_Article_IEq23.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> the timestamp of the <inline-formula id="IEq24"><alternatives><tex-math id="M47">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
