      <p id="Par83">Finally, for all the samples of the previous examples, we simulated an Illumina HiSeq 2500 paired-end sequencing experiment, with 100 average reads per cell, mean read length <inline-formula id="IEq93"><alternatives><tex-math id="M179">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
